Apple <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/09/09/everything-apple-announced-september-2025-event/">announced</a> the new Apple Watch lineup earlier this week, including the Apple Watch Series 11, Apple Watch SE 3, and Apple Watch Ultra 3. If you're planning to pre-order the Ultra 3, <a href="https://bestbuy.7tiv.net/dOgDNQ"><strong>Best Buy is offering a &#36;50 discount</strong></a> to its members this week.<br/>
<br/>
