<br/>
To get this deal, you need to be a <a href="https://bestbuy.7tiv.net/LKBoX3">My Best Buy Plus or Total</a> member, and when you <a href="https://bestbuy.7tiv.net/K0mPaa">add the smartwatch to your cart</a> you'll automatically see the &#36;50 discount applied. This knocks the price of the brand new device down to &#36;749.00, from &#36;799.00.<br/>
<br/>
